{
  "texts": [
    "This adaptability helps in meeting the varied needs of students, promoting inclusivity in education.",
    "ChatGPT can also assist students while building algorithms, code debugging and code optimization if used properly (Yilmaz & Yilmaz, 2023a).",
    "This can increase positively influence their learning outcomes, self-confidence, and motivation toward programming courses (Bravo & Cruz-Bohorquez, 2024; Yilmaz & Yilmaz, 2023a).",
    "Despite its advantages, the use of ChatGPT in programming education has come with its challenges.",
    "Concerns regarding the accuracy of information provided, potential over-reliance on the tool, risk of plagiarism, and social inequities to access AI-features are some of the challenges associated with the use of ChatGPT (Bringula, 2024; Bucaioni et al., 2024; Silva et al., 2024; Lo, 2023)."
  ]
}